
URL = http://SlideWiki.org

=Description=

"SlideWiki.org is a platform for OpenCourseWare authoring and publishing. Similar as Wikipedia allows the collaborative authoring of encyclopedic texts, GitHub of sourceode or OpenStreetMaps of maps, SlideWiki enables communities to create comprehensive open educational resources. SlideWiki is open-source software and all content in SlideWiki is Open Knowledge."

